---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Handwriting Recognition & Writing"
  description="A pyramidal parallel manipulator system integrating CNN, image processing, and motion control for handwritten character recognition and automatic writing."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container research-detail">
      <a class="back-link" href="/">&larr; Back to Home</a>

      <header class="detail-header">
        <h1 class="detail-title">Integrated Development of a Parallel Manipulator with Deep Learning — A Case Study on Handwritten Character Recognition and Writing</h1>
        <p class="detail-subtitle">
          A pyramidal parallel manipulator system integrating CNN-based recognition and robotic writing.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Overview -->
      <h2 class="detail-heading">Overview</h2>
      <p class="detail-paragraph">
        This research develops a system built on a pyramidal parallel manipulator that integrates
        mechanical design, motion control, image processing, and deep learning to perform
        handwritten character recognition and automatic writing. A camera first captures
        handwritten images; a convolutional neural network built with Keras then recognizes the
        English letters and digits; finally, the recognition results are transmitted to the robotic
        arm via MQTT, driving the manipulator along predefined trajectories to complete the
        writing task. Experimental results show that the system reliably recognizes handwritten
        characters and successfully writes text such as "TKU".
      </p>

      <!-- Video -->
      <h2 class="detail-heading">Research Video</h2>
      <div class="video-wrapper">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mkzCl1BCUgY"
          title="Handwriting Recognition & Writing — Research Video"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>

      <!-- Core Technologies -->
      <h2 class="detail-heading">Core Technologies</h2>
      <ul class="tech-tags">
        <li class="tech-tag">CNN Handwriting Recognition</li>
        <li class="tech-tag">OpenCV Image Processing</li>
        <li class="tech-tag">Matlab Trajectory Planning</li>
        <li class="tech-tag">MQTT Communication</li>
        <li class="tech-tag">Delta Robot Control</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Research Highlights -->
      <h2 class="detail-heading">Research Highlights</h2>
      <ul class="highlight-list">
        <li class="highlight-item">
          <strong>Cross-domain integration:</strong> Combines deep learning, machine vision,
          robotic manipulation, motion control, and communication technologies into a complete
          recognition-to-execution pipeline.
        </li>
        <li class="highlight-item">
          <strong>Deep-learning recognition:</strong> A CNN model built with Python, OpenCV, and
          Keras, trained to recognize handwritten digits (0–9) and uppercase letters (A–Z).
        </li>
        <li class="highlight-item">
          <strong>Model performance:</strong> Trained on 331,837 samples and validated on 110,613
          samples, achieving 97.34% recognition accuracy.
        </li>
        <li class="highlight-item">
          <strong>Physical system validation:</strong> Recognition results are transmitted to the
          manipulator via MQTT, and a parallel robotic arm physically completes the writing.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Related Publications -->
      <h2 class="detail-heading">Related Publications</h2>
      <ul class="pub-list">
        <li class="pub-item">
          <strong>S.-T. Wang</strong>, I.-H. Li and W.-Y. Wang,
          "Implementation of A Pyramidal Manipulator for Handwritten Character Recognition and
          Writing Using CNN,"
          <em>iRobotics Journal</em>, vol. 6, no. 1, 2023.
        </li>
        <li class="pub-item">
          The 29th International Conference on Fuzzy Theory and Its Applications, 2021.
        </li>
        <li class="pub-item">
          The 27th International Conference on Fuzzy Theory and Its Applications, 2019.
        </li>
        <li class="pub-item">
          Ministry of Science and Technology Undergraduate Research Project,
          "Integrated Development of a Parallel Manipulator with Deep Learning — A Case Study on
          Handwritten Character Recognition and Writing," 2019.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .research-detail {
    max-width: 52rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .detail-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .detail-eyebrow {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .detail-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .detail-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .detail-heading {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .detail-paragraph {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  /* Video embed (responsive 16:9) */
  .video-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%;
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--color-card-shadow);
  }

  .video-wrapper iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  /* Tech tags */
  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .tech-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
    background-color: var(--color-tag-bg);
    color: var(--color-tag-text);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  }

  /* Highlights */
  .highlight-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .highlight-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .highlight-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.7em;
    width: 0.4rem;
    height: 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .highlight-item strong {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Publication list */
  .pub-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .pub-item {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .pub-item strong {
    color: var(--color-heading);
  }

  .pub-item em {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
</style>
